metadata.name: Telomere #001
metadata.description:
Telomere is the structure at the end of eukaryotic chromosomes.
"Telomeres" is a series of photographs after it ,taken in 2008 by photographer Katsu Nagaishi.
Based on the concept of "preserving eternal beauty",  a number of pressed flowers are encapsulated in acrylic boxes.
This time, "Telomere" has been reborn as NFT Photograph.
